  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city skyline at dusk or dawn, illuminated by warm and cool tones. The scene features a sprawling urban landscape with numerous lights twinkling across the city, stretching towards a large body of water. Several bridges span the water, connecting different parts of the urban area. The foreground is dominated by a dark, hilly landscape with trees, silhouetted against the brighter city lights. The sky transitions from a deep blue at the top to vibrant orange and yellow hues near the horizon, creating a dramatic and serene atmosphere. The overall impression is one of vastness and beauty, capturing the energy of a vibrant city against the backdrop of a natural landscape.",
